On 10/24/2012 3:21 PM, Mark Hanson wrote:
> I just had a brain fart, how about an EV link with *all* our EV's, each E=
V goes a distance in their state and passes a baton (or something) to the n=
ext guy and that baton ends up on the other coast.

I like it! :-) Each person "in the middle" gets to meet two other EVers, =

and see their EVs.

Instead of a baton, maybe "pass the battery"? Each person could sign it =

as it passes. By signing, he's also confirming that the person that =

brought it to him, and the person he passed it to also arrive in EVs =

(and not a HumVee).

